{
  "dialogue": {
    "Hello, it's nice to meet you.": ["Introduction"],
    "You picked a good time to move here... The spring is lovely.": [
      "Introduction_sv1"
    ],
    "Oh, wow... I had a sip of this stuff when I was a kid, and I've never forgotten the taste.": [
      "AcceptGift_StardropTea"
    ],
    "Hey, thanks a bunch, @! This makes my birthday feel special.": [
      "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive"
    ],
    "You want to dance with me? Yes!": ["FlowerDance_Accept"],
    "I was wondering if you'd ask me...": ["FlowerDance_Accept_sv1"],
    "I had a feeling you would ask me...": ["dating_Leah"],
    "Elliott's a real romantic... I'm sure your days will be filled with poetry!": [
      "married_Elliott"
    ],
    "I'm happy that Shane's in such a good place. I've never seen him smile so much!": [
      "married_Shane"
    ],
    "With his love for chickens, I'm sure he'll fit right in on %farm Farm!": [
      "married_Shane_sv1"
    ],
    "Oh! Thank you! This one has an interesting shape...": ["AcceptGift_169"],
    "Hey, where'd you find that? *sniff*... Mmm... This will be perfect, grated over a fresh pasta. Thank you!": [
      "AcceptGift_430"
    ],
    "Mmm... Back in the city, the veggies never tasted this fresh. I love it!": [
      "AcceptGift_200"
    ],
    "This looks delicious... Thank you! There's nothing quite like a fresh, wild salad.": [
      "AcceptGift_196_chance_1"
    ],
    "Oh, wow, @! This is exactly what I was craving! How'd you know?": [
      "AcceptGift_196_chance_2"
    ],
    "Please don't feel like you have to spend all your time with me now that we're dating... I know you're a busy person!": [
      "dating_Leah_memory_oneday"
    ],
    "I sold enough art at that show to get by for another year... that's all I needed!": [
      "eventSeen_53_memory_oneday"
    ],
    "I'm still fuming about the picnic... what a weirdo!": [
      "eventSeen_54_memory_oneday"
    ],
    "Let's never talk about... that person... ever again.": [
      "eventSeen_54_memory_oneday_sv1"
    ],
    "If my art continues to sell online like it has, I'll be able to keep making art forever. That's always been my dream.": [
      "eventSeen_584059_memory_oneday"
    ],
    "Don't tell anyone, but Willy let me steer the boat for a few minutes.": [
      "Resort_Entering"
    ],
    "Well, that was deeply relaxing.": ["Resort_Leaving"],
    "I love the weather in Stardew Valley, but seeing a different climate now and then helps put things into perspective.": [
      "Resort"
    ],
    "The shape of the waves here is awe inspiring.": ["Resort_Shore"],
    "I wonder if I could ever capture that sort of formlessness in a sculpture.": [
      "Resort_Shore_sv1"
    ],
    "I like the heat as long as I'm keeping perfectly still.": ["Resort_Chair"],
    "Mmm, I bet the trees around here would make for an interesting medium to work with.": [
      "Resort_Wander"
    ],
    "Though Willy probably wouldn't be happy with me if I dragged a bunch of logs onto his ship!": [
      "Resort_Wander_sv1"
    ],
    "I wonder what kind of things you could forage out here.": [
      "Resort_Wander_2"
    ],
    "I think I saw some tasty looking walnuts growing on a bush nearby.": [
      "Resort_Wander_2_sv1"
    ],
    "Have you tried the Pi\u00c3\u00b1a Colada? I'm on my second one... hehe.": [
      "Resort_Bar"
    ],
    "Finally! I was starting to get worried you wanted to dance with someone else!": [
      "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse"
    ],
    "I'll be honest. I don't want to dance with you.": ["FlowerDance_Decline"],
    "I've realized I'm happier by myself. So just leave me be.": ["divorced"],
    "Ohh... Got it. Hah... I really don't have any luck when it comes to this stuff...": [
      "breakUp"
    ],
    "I don't want to see you for a while...": ["dumped_Girls"],
    "You caused a lot of grief with what you did... but I'm ready to put the past behind us.": [
      "secondChance_Girls"
    ],
    "I came for the sound of the ocean. Beautiful, isn't it?": ["Beach"],
    "The trees look nice today, don't they?": ["Mon"],
    "So why did you become a farmer?": ["Mon_sv1"],
    "So are you making as much money as you hoped?": ["Mon_old_prereq_1"],
    "Spending time in nature is very rewarding.": ["Mon_old_prereq_2"],
    "Hmm. That seems kind of shallow, doesn't it?": ["Mon_21"],
    "That's pretty much the reason I came here, too!": ["Mon_22"],
    "That's very sweet to honor your grandfather like that.": ["Mon_211132"],
    "Where did all these plants come from? It's a surprise, but I'm not complaining...": [
      "GreenRain"
    ],
    "I guess everyone in town was scared of that strange rain? I had no idea... I just thought it was incredible!": [
      "GreenRainFinished"
    ],
    "Imagine if this rain lasted all summer... The plants would take over the entire valley!": [
      "GreenRain_2"
    ],
    "Hi. Oh, you want to talk?": ["Tue4"],
    "The landscape around here gives me a lot of ideas. The terrain is almost like a sculpture itself.": [
      "Tue4_sv1"
    ],
    "I don't make art for money. It's just an urge that I have.": ["Tue4_sv2"],
    "Farming seems like a very rewarding profession. You get to create delicious food for everyone!": [
      "Tue4_sv3"
    ],
    "You're probably busy. Sorry.": ["Tue4_sv4"],
    "Hello, neighbor.": ["Tue"],
    "We both live outside of town. Does that mean something?": ["Tue_sv1"],
    "This morning I accidentally stepped on a bug.": ["Wed_chance_1"],
    "Sometimes I think it's impossible to live without destroying nature in some way.": [
      "Wed_chance_2"
    ],
    "I love being around animals. They're so innocent.": ["Wed6"],
    "Farm animals are wonderful, too.": ["Wed6_sv1"],
    "It must be satisfying to harvest a whole field of crops, huh? You're basically creating food out of nothing!": [
      "Wed8_query_1"
    ],
    "Hi @! I was just thinking about you and your farm.": ["Wed8_query_2"],
    "I was imagining how good it must feel to harvest a big bunch of crops.": [
      "Wed8_query_2_sv1"
    ],
    "Wouldn't it be nice to have help, though?": ["Wed8_query_2_sv2"],
    "There's actually a lot of wild food in this area, if you know where to look.": [
      "Thu"
    ],
    "I've been having fresh salads almost every day.": ["Thu_sv1"],
    "Foraging is a specialty of mine. Someday I'll make you a fresh salad.": [
      "Thu6"
    ],
    "It's simpler to be friends with the trees. They don't have much to say.": [
      "Fri"
    ],
    "We wouldn't be able to survive without nature. It's good to remember that.": [
      "Fri2"
    ],
    "Hello, @. It's a nice day, isn't it?": ["Fri4"],
    "Stop by my cabin if you ever need someone to talk to.": [
      "Fri4_sv1",
      "summer_Fri6_sv1",
      "fall_Fri6"
    ],
    "Sometimes, a strange feeling comes over me. My head becomes totally empty... and I feel completely at peace, even blissful.": [
      "Fri6"
    ],
    "Hey, now! It has nothing to do with drinking wine!": ["Fri6_sv1"],
    "Do you ever wonder what it's like to be a different person?": ["Fri8"],
    "Do our thoughts manifest in a similar way, or is it radically different?": [
      "Fri8_sv1"
    ],
    "Don't mind me, I think about weird things sometimes...": ["Fri8_sv2"],
    "I love to decorate for the different seasons.": ["Sat"],
    "I've thought about growing some crops, but I think I'd feel bad having to clear out all the wild plants to make space.": [
      "Sat8_query_1"
    ],
    "Farming sounds so fun. I want to try it, someday.": ["Sat8_query_2"],
    "If you hear any banging from inside my hut, it's probably just me working on one of my sculptures.": [
      "Sun"
    ],
    "If you ever find any interesting looking driftwood, I could use it.": [
      "Sun8"
    ],
    "It would be special that you gave it to me.": ["Sun8_sv1"],
    "...What?": ["event_sculpt1"],
    "Oh! Yeah, that's absolutely right!": ["event_sculpt1_sv1"],
    "There's nothing wrong with that... I think there's lots of beauty to be found in raw, untouched nature!": [
      "event_sculpt2"
    ],
    "But as a human, I'm also interested in how we shape and interpret the world around us... I guess what I'm saying is that I'm interested in 'art'.": [
      "event_sculpt2_sv1"
    ],
    "You pig!%fork": ["event_sculpt3_male_farmer"],
    "Oh! You're...? Me too.": ["event_sculpt3_female_farmer"],
    "Get out!": ["event_sculpt3_sv1_male_farmer"],
    "That's good to know.": ["event_sculpt3_sv1_female_farmer"],
    "You're right... I just wouldn't have been happy back there.": [
      "event_parents1"
    ],
    "It was better for both of us... to end an unsustainable relationship while we were still young and flexible.": [
      "event_parents1_sv1"
    ],
    "That's a little harsh... but, yeah. We had different priorities.": [
      "event_parents2"
    ],
    "Oh yeah? Well maybe I'll just leave, then!%fork": ["event_parents3"],
    "*sigh*...": ["event_parents4", "event_parents5"],
    "I guess you're right... it was kind of selfish. But can you really blame me for wanting to be happy? Ugh... I don't know...": [
      "event_parents4_sv1"
    ],
    "Maybe you're right... Humans are selfish creatures. I don't know.": [
      "event_parents5_sv1"
    ],
    "I probably shouldn't dwell on it. We all have to make hard choices from time to time.": [
      "event_parents5_sv2"
    ],
    "You can tell it's summer by the sweet smell of nectar wafting through the air!": [
      "summer_1"
    ],
    "I found some wild fruits this morning!": ["summer_Mon"],
    "Sorry, I don't have any left.": ["summer_Mon_sv1"],
    "Keep looking, I'm sure you'll find something.": ["summer_Mon_sv2"],
    "The sound of farm animals is great, isn't it?": ["summer_Tue"],
    "The simple things in life are best: a soft summer breeze, majestic clouds, and a goblet full of Stardew Valley red.": [
      "summer_Tue4"
    ],
    "I have a good eye for wild fruit. Some day I'll make you a nice fruit salad.": [
      "summer_Thu6"
    ],
    "You can use a tapper to harvest syrups and other useful liquids directly from trees.": [
      "summer_Fri"
    ],
    "It's a slow process, but the result can be quite valuable.": [
      "summer_Fri_sv1"
    ],
    "I hate to be blunt, but if we don't treat nature with respect, our grandchildren will be doomed.": [
      "summer_Fri2"
    ],
    "Don't you think so?": ["summer_Fri2_sv1"],
    "Do you ever walk out into the forest... Pause... And simply enjoy the beauty of nature?": [
      "summer_Fri4"
    ],
    "It's easy to forget how incredible this world actually is...": [
      "summer_Fri4_sv1"
    ],
    "Hello, @. Do you ever get lonely on that big farm?": ["summer_Fri6"],
    "The flowing water keeps my house a little bit cooler in summer.": [
      "summer_Sat"
    ],
    "I can't tolerate heat very well.": ["summer_Sat_sv1"],
    "One Summer, it was so hot during the night that I got out of bed and jumped into the river!": [
      "summer_Sat4"
    ],
    "I hope no one saw me!": ["summer_Sat4_sv1"],
    "What should I do on such a warm, lazy day? *sigh*": ["summer_Sun"],
    "Any ideas?": ["summer_Sun_sv1"],
    "How quickly the seasons change!": ["fall_1"],
    "It's shocking.": ["fall_1_sv1"],
    "I found some wild mushrooms over the weekend!": ["fall_Mon_chance_1"],
    "I had a huge plate of wild mushrooms and eggs for breakfast today... I'm still full.": [
      "fall_Mon_chance_2"
    ],
    "Keep your nose to the ground and you'll find some mushrooms yourself... I'm sure of it.": [
      "fall_Mon_sv1"
    ],
    "I wonder if I could make a collage out of dried leaves?": ["fall_Tue"],
    "They're just so colorful... I can't help but think of the potential for art projects.": [
      "fall_Tue_sv1"
    ],
    "Everyone has a unique and interesting perspective, whether they believe it or not. Don't you think so?": [
      "fall_Tue4"
    ],
    "Although, some people have opinions that I just can't respect.": [
      "fall_Tue4_sv1"
    ],
    "It's so nice to live by the river.": ["fall_Wed"],
    "I fall asleep to the soothing sound of water every night.": [
      "fall_Wed_sv1"
    ],
    "One of these days I'll have to make you a wild mushroom stir-fry.": [
      "fall_Thu6"
    ],
    "Do you have a kitchen in your house?": ["fall_Fri"],
    "If you have a kitchen, you can cook all kinds of delicious meals.": [
      "fall_Fri_sv1"
    ],
    "Decorations accentuate the feeling of the season. I think it's a worthwhile tradition.": [
      "fall_Sat"
    ],
    "There's a lot of good places to walk around here.": ["fall_Sun"],
    "It feels good to stretch your legs.": ["fall_Sun_sv1"],
    "One thing I love about this place is that there are beautiful waterfalls.": [
      "fall_Sun4"
    ],
    "Do you ever spend time watching them? It's soothing...": ["fall_Sun4_sv1"],
    "I love the way everything looks when it's covered with fresh snow.": [
      "winter_Mon"
    ],
    "It gets pretty cold in my little cabin.": ["winter_Tue"],
    "I just snuggle up under a huge blanket, and I'm okay.": ["winter_Tue_sv1"],
    "I saw a snow rabbit early this morning! They're rare, aren't they?": [
      "winter_Wed"
    ],
    "I'm having a hard time finding fresh food to eat.": ["winter_Thu"],
    "I've been eating a lot of bread.": ["winter_Thu_sv1"],
    "*Sigh*... It's hard to get fresh food in the winter.": ["winter_Thu6"],
    "I bet your farm is pretty well stocked with food, huh?": [
      "winter_Thu6_sv1"
    ],
    "Time seems to move slower here.": ["winter_Fri"],
    "When I lived in the city, the year went by so fast.": ["winter_Fri_sv1"],
    "Do you ever get cold in that farmhouse of yours?": ["winter_Fri6"],
    "Stop by my cabin if you want to huddle under one of my quilts and drink cider.": [
      "winter_Fri6_sv1"
    ],
    "Hello. Do you want something?": ["winter_Sat"],
    "Hello, @. Is there something you wanted to talk about?": ["winter_Sat2"],
    "Do you ever take a whole day off?": ["winter_Sun"],
    "It's a refreshing break.": ["winter_Sun_sv1"],
    "You should take a whole day off, now and then.": ["winter_Sun4"],
    "Not only is it good for the soul, but in the long run, you'll actually be more productive!": [
      "winter_Sun4_sv1"
    ]
  },
  "marriage_dialogue": {
    "I sometimes find inspiration in the most unlikely of places.": [
      "Rainy_Day_0"
    ],
    "I used to find rain depressing when I lived in the city. But here in Stardew Valley it's beautiful.": [
      "Rainy_Day_1"
    ],
    "Good morning! I got up early and did some mushroom hunting. Here, take one.": [
      "Rainy_Day_2"
    ],
    "Searching for mushrooms is like going on a treasure hunt. It's a lot of fun.": [
      "Rainy_Day_2_sv1"
    ],
    "It's days like this I'm really happy about my heavy-duty boots.": [
      "Rainy_Day_3"
    ],
    "The trees have been begging for this rain... I'm happy for them.": [
      "Rainy_Day_4"
    ],
    "How was your day? Did you see any animals out there?": ["Rainy_Night_0"],
    "Don't look too close, it's a work in progress.": ["patio_Leah"],
    "I usually go for salad... but a wet night like this gives me cravings for hot soup.": [
      "Rainy_Night_1"
    ],
    "It's going to be relaxing to fall asleep on a night like this...": [
      "Rainy_Night_2"
    ],
    "I made a little wood sculpture today, but it was so ugly I threw it into the fire.": [
      "Rainy_Night_3"
    ],
    "I think to become a great artist, you have to be critical of your own work.": [
      "Rainy_Night_3_sv1"
    ],
    "I'm glad you're home... It's a good night to get under the covers and stay warm.": [
      "Rainy_Night_4"
    ],
    "How was your day today, dear? Muddy?": ["Rainy_Night_Leah"],
    "This house is a lot nicer than my old cabin! I don't miss it.": [
      "Indoor_Day_0"
    ],
    "Good morning, @. I've planted these in a little pot out back...": [
      "Indoor_Day_1"
    ],
    "I grew that with great love and attention. Enjoy it.": [
      "Indoor_Day_1_sv1"
    ],
    "Always remember to keep your eyes peeled for wild food! There's lots out there.": [
      "Indoor_Day_2"
    ],
    "I was thinking... life's too short to eat bad food. Luckily, we live in one of the best regions for fresh greens and vegetables!": [
      "Indoor_Day_3"
    ],
    "Here, I made you a healthy salad.": ["Indoor_Day_3_sv1"],
    "I'm surprised you aren't sick of my salad yet!": ["Indoor_Day_3_sv2"],
    "Good morning, @! I made us some coffee.": ["Indoor_Day_4"],
    "My morning just wouldn't be complete without a hot cup of coffee.": [
      "Indoor_Day_4_sv1"
    ],
    "Something about this time of night makes me thirsty.": ["Indoor_Night_0"],
    "The flow of time is so delicate... even the tiniest decision changes the future forever.": [
      "Indoor_Night_1"
    ],
    "It's so much lovelier here at night than the garish glow of the city.": [
      "Indoor_Night_2"
    ],
    "Everything worked out perfectly for me. I'm very lucky.": [
      "Indoor_Night_2_sv1"
    ],
    "I never thought I'd receive a mermaid's pendant so soon after moving here! I'm happy about it, though.": [
      "Indoor_Night_3"
    ],
    "I saw a wild rabbit today. I just wish I could pet one someday. They look so soft...": [
      "Indoor_Night_4"
    ],
    "The cool breeze feels nice. It reminds me of living by the river.": [
      "Outdoor_0"
    ],
    "Hmm... I'm going to do some maintenance over here. I just get the urge to do some hammering now and then.": [
      "Outdoor_1"
    ],
    "It's going to be a special day, I can sense it.": ["Outdoor_2"],
    "Ah... that smell of fresh dirt. There's nothing quite like it.": [
      "Outdoor_3"
    ],
    "You can just tell the air is clean here... it feels good in the lungs.": [
      "Outdoor_3_sv1"
    ],
    "Don't overwork yourself, dear.": ["Outdoor_4"],
    "Make sure and take a break every now and then, or get something to eat.": [
      "Outdoor_4_sv1"
    ],
    "I'm going to take a nature walk today. I need to get out of the house.": [
      "funLeave_Leah"
    ],
    "I had a nice, relaxing time today. How did your day go?": [
      "funReturn_Leah"
    ],
    "It's fun to be a parent. I want to make sure %kid1 grows up to have a love for the outdoors.": [
      "OneKid_3"
    ],
    "We've got a wonderful farm and a full family. Our new life has really turned out well, hasn't it?": [
      "TwoKids_3"
    ],
    "Living here, I feel like I'm on the summit of a great mountain.": [
      "Good_0"
    ],
    "Did I ever tell you... when you first moved here I had a dream that we'd be together someday.": [
      "Good_1"
    ],
    "Sometimes it's hard not to believe in destiny... the fact that I decided to move here, and that we found each other.": [
      "Good_2"
    ],
    "It could've gone entirely differently at any point.": ["Good_2_sv1"],
    "Wow, you look full of energy today!": ["Good_3_male_farmer"],
    "You look beautiful today.": ["Good_3_female_farmer"],
    "Mmm... You smell nice today.": ["Good_4"],
    "I was just admiring my wedding amulet... I'll cherish this treasure for the rest of my life.": [
      "Good_5"
    ],
    "Be careful out there! Sometimes I worry about you falling into a mine shaft.": [
      "Good_6"
    ],
    "@? I just want to say that I appreciate all the hard work you do for our household.": [
      "Good_7"
    ],
    "Don't worry about me... I know you've got a lot of responsibilities outside of the house. I'm fine in here by myself!": [
      "Good_8"
    ],
    "Oh, I'm not bored... I'm just enjoying what we have here.": ["Good_9"],
    "It's a simple life, but I like it.": ["Good_9_sv1"],
    "I hope you'll still like me when I'm old and gray.": ["Neutral_0"],
    "I wonder who lived here before us?": ["Neutral_1"],
    "Don't you have anything to do today?": ["Neutral_2"],
    "If you go into town, make sure and say hi to everyone for me.": [
      "Neutral_3"
    ],
    "I'll do the laundry tomorrow morning before you get up... that way you won't have any down-time.": [
      "Neutral_4"
    ],
    "Are we doing okay on money, @?": ["Neutral_5"],
    "I wonder what everyone in town is doing today?": ["Neutral_6"],
    "I don't really feel like doing anything today.": ["Neutral_7"],
    "No matter how much I clean, the house keeps getting dirty again.": [
      "Neutral_8"
    ],
    "I guess farms can be kind of dirty.": ["Neutral_8_sv1"],
    "I wonder if we'll live here our entire lives?": ["Neutral_9"],
    "...Do you still love me?": ["Bad_0"],
    "*sigh*... Maybe we got married too young.": ["Bad_1"],
    "Are you still happy with me?": ["Bad_2"],
    "Did I do something wrong? You've been acting different lately.": ["Bad_3"],
    "Do you ever wonder what else is out there?": ["Bad_4"],
    "You used to be romantic... what happened?": ["Bad_5"],
    "I know I'm not as young as I used to be... is that what you married me for?": [
      "Bad_5_sv1"
    ],
    "We only have one short life to live... is this the best way to do it?": [
      "Bad_6"
    ],
    "I used to be your sweetie... now you only seem to put up with me when I make a hot dinner.": [
      "Bad_7"
    ],
    "You've been so cold to me lately...": ["Bad_8"],
    "I wonder if I could've done better.": ["Bad_9"],
    "So, what are we planting this season?": ["spring_2"],
    "That was some way to ring in the new year last night...": ["spring_1"],
    "*sigh*... I guess it's time for the 'spring cleaning' again.": [
      "spring_15"
    ],
    "Ah, summer... I can smell the spice berries already.": ["summer_1"],
    "Sorry if I'm wet to the touch... I was sweating all night in the heat.": [
      "summer_9"
    ],
    "It's summer... that means the house is full of flies.": ["summer_2"],
    "Don't worry, I'll take care of them.": ["summer_2_sv1"],
    "I love fall for the mushroom hunting opportunities. It comes and goes pretty fast.": [
      "fall_1"
    ],
    "Have you planned for winter at all? It's good to have a stockpile of hay.": [
      "fall_20"
    ],
    "I know harvest season is a busy time for you. I'll try and help out as much as I can.": [
      "fall_2"
    ],
    "Winter's here, and that means crystal fruit is in season. It has such a unique flavor, don't you think?": [
      "winter_1"
    ],
    "I'm looking forward to carving ice sculptures tomorrow. I only get to do it once a year, but it's a lot of fun!": [
      "winter_7"
    ],
    "Hey, here's to another great year at %farm farm! Let's have some fun tonight!": [
      "winter_28"
    ],
    "Next year is going to be great, I can feel it.": ["winter_28_sv1"]
  },
  "gift_tastes": {
    "Oh! This is exactly what I wanted! Thank you!": ["LeahGiftTaste_1"],
    "This is a really nice gift! Thank you!": ["LeahGiftTaste_2"],
    "Hmm... I guess everyone has different tastes.": ["LeahGiftTaste_3"],
    "This is a pretty terrible gift, isn't it?": ["LeahGiftTaste_4"],
    "Thank you.": ["LeahGiftTaste_5"]
  },
  "misc": {
    "You're the new farmer, aren't you?": ["WipedMemory"],
    "You seem... no. I'm sure we've never met.": ["WipedMemory_sv1"],
    "This... Are you trying to hurt me even more?": ["Divorced_bouquet"],
    "I don't want your gift.": ["Divorced_gift"],
    "I've heard there's some really beautiful nature footage in this one... I'm really looking forward to it": [
      "Leah_spring_movie_1_BeforeMovie"
    ],
    "That was great. I'm pretty sure I even saw my cabin in one of those Stardew Valley aerial shots!": [
      "Leah_spring_movie_1_AfterMovie"
    ],
    "I'm really intrigued by this movie... I'm a sucker for the mysterious.": [
      "Leah_love_BeforeMovie"
    ],
    "That was great! The narrative was very loose, but I think it was intended to speak to the emotions, not the intellect.": [
      "Leah_love_AfterMovie"
    ],
    "I'm not sure what to expect with this movie, but I'm going to keep an open mind!": [
